name: YTLitePlus
localizedDescription:
YTLite with more features!

YTLitePlus is an enhanced Youtube app that offers a superior Youtube experience, combining YTLite (by @dayanch96) with numerous other tweaks :

• YTLite
• YTUHD
• YouPiP
• YTABConfig
• YouMute
• DontEatMyContent
• Return YouTube Dislikes
• iSponsorBlock
• YouRememberCaption
• YTNoTracking
• YTUnShorts
• YTNoCheckLocalNetwork
• BigYTMiniPlayer
• YTSpeed
• YTHoldForSpeed
• YTVideoOverlay
• YouQuality
• YTNoModernUI
• OLEDDarkmode
• OLDDarkmode
• LowContrastMode
• YTNoSuggestedVideo

name: StravaPremium
localizedDescription:
App that transforms fitness tracking into a social hub, enabling you to record activities, discover routes, build community support, train smarter, ensure safety, sync devices, join challenges, and share real efforts—all in one place. A user requested it so here it is.
Last updated: 09-08-2024
Status: ✅ ⭐

name: uYouPlus (uYou+)
localizedDescription:
uYouPlus is a modified version of uYou with some extra features! (requires iOS 14.0 and later).

Full infomation about uYouPlus (uYou+) is available on my Github: https://github.com/qnblackcat/uYouPlus/

Credits: Please keep the Credits if you re-up uYouPlus! 
https://github.com/qnblackcat/uYouPlus#credits

Attention:
- If you like the app, considering support the developers!
- YTUHD is not stable atm. You might encounter stuttering, heat, battery drain..., especially when playing at 2160p (4K) quality. However, this should not happen if you use TrollStore.
- Unless you're using TrollStore, deep-link (aka Open in the YouTube App) simply will not work.

Known issues:
- uYou's issues: https://github.com/MiRO92/uYou-for-YouTube/issues
- uYouPlus's issues: https://github.com/qnblackcat/uYouPlus
